Whereas Yeardley Love of Baltimore, Maryland, was an exceptional person and lacrosse player, who
			 wore the number one, and was the tragic victim of relationship violence
			 while in college at the University of Virginia;

Whereas the vision of the One Love Foundation is to keep Yeardley’s spirit alive by promoting
			 strength of character as the premise of all of the foundation’s numerous
			 programs;

paragraph.text:
focuses on heightening awareness and making new commitments to stop relationship violence in our
			 immediate circle of family, friends, neighbors, schools, and
